Package: playOmics
Type: Package
Title: A multi-omics pipeline for biomarker discovery
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Jagoda Glowacka-Walas
Maintainer: Jagoda Glowacka-Walas <jagaaa92@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides a suite of tools for the comprehensive analysis and visualization 
    of multi-omics datasets. It facilitates data cleaning, integration, and preprocessing; statistical analysis and modeling; 
    and detailed interpretability of models using SHAP values and interactive visualizations via a Shiny application interface. 
    Key features include streamlined workflow for data input, feature selection, model creation, performance logging, 
    and an MLOps-oriented approach for model deployment. The package emphasizes open science principles, ensuring 
    reproducibility and transparency in multi-omics data analysis.
